      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "second-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Corinthians 3:10",
      "text": "ܐܝܟ ܗܘ ܓܝܪ ܕܐܦܠܐ ܡܫܒܚܐ ܗܝ ܕܐܫܬܒܚܬ ܒܦܘܚܡܐ ܕܗܢܐ ܫܘܒܚܐ ܡܝܬܪܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
