      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "second-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Corinthians 3:12",
      "text": "ܡܛܠ ܕܐܝܬ ܠܢ ܗܟܝܠ ܗܢܐ ܤܒܪܐ ܝܬܝܪܐܝܬ ܒܓܠܐ ܥܝܢ ܡܬܕܒܪܝܢܢ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
