      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "second-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Corinthians 3:16",
      "text": "ܘܐܡܬܝ ܕܐܢܫ ܡܢܗܘܢ ܢܬܦܢܐ ܠܘܬ ܡܪܝܐ ܡܫܬܩܠܐ ܡܢܗ ܬܚܦܝܬܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
